# Wallpapers Directory
# Place your wallpapers here after installation.
# 
# Required files for full functionality:
# - 6.mp4 (or any video) - Main desktop video wallpaper
# - lockvideo.mp4 - Lock screen transition video
# - lock_wallpaper.png - Lock screen background
#
# Optional:
# - Any .png, .jpg, .gif files for random_wallpaper.sh script
#
# Recommended cyberpunk wallpapers sources:
# - https://wallhaven.cc/search?q=cyberpunk
# - https://www.reddit.com/r/wallpapers/
# - https://unsplash.com/s/photos/cyberpunk
